        cloudflare-dynamic-dns-client - Cloudflare Dynamic DNS Client

Dynamic DNS Client for Cloudflare.

INSTALLATION

    Install Cloudflare Dynamic DNS Client.

      make install

CONFIGURATION

    Change email (Cloudflare email address), key (Cloudflare Global API Key) and zone
    (Cloudflare DNS zone) in the configuration file.  Hostname, zone_id and
    dns_record_id are optional.

  - /etc/cloudflare-dynamic-dns-client.conf

USAGE

    Run the client manually or enable the systemd timer.

  - Manually:

      cloudflare-dynamic-dns-client

  - Systemd timer:

      systemctl enable --now cloudflare-dynamic-dns-client.timer
